        What Happens to the Rental Bond When You Sell a Tenanted Brisbane Property
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The bond stays with the RTA, but both the seller and buyer have steps to complete at settlement. Here is how the handover works under Queensland tenancy law.
      </p>
